comments: Reaves (LAL) moves alongside Nesmith's (IND) path with a collapsed forearm and marginal body contact occurs as he cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt.
Turner (IND) blocks the shot attempt after the ball makes contact with the backboard and has a chance to score.
Turner (IND) establishes screening position in Reddish's (LAL) path and marginal foot to foot contact occurs as the pick is set.
Turner (IND) cleanly blocks Reaves' (LAL) shot attempt before the ball touches the backboard.
Davis (LAL) doesn't give Siakam (IND) a step to avoid his obtained defensive position and illegal body contact occurs at the start of the drive.
Turner (IND) reaches in and avoids making arm contact with Davis (LAL) as he attempts to get to the pass.
James (LAL) brings his arm toward Siakam's (IND) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
James (LAL) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Siakam (IND) prior to incidental arm contact occurring during the driving shot attempt.
Siakam (IND) slightly moves to his right as he establishes screening position in Reaves' (LAL) path and marginal contact occurs as the screen is set.
Nembhard (IND) does not intentionally redirect the ball after the made basket.
Siakam (IND) wraps both arms around Reaves (LAL), and initiates contact that affects his FOM during the screen.
Toppin (IND) commits a take foul on Davis (LAL).
Sheppard (IND) commits a take foul on Reaves (LAL).
Nembhard (IND) reaches in and initiates illegal contact with Reaves' (LAL) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Nembhard (IND) extends both hands forward and initiates illegal contact with Reaves (LAL), which affects his SQBR.
McDermott (IND) extends both hands forward and initiates contact with Dinwiddie (LAL), which affects his SQBR.
Toppin (IND) commits a take foul on Reddish (LAL).
